%% OpenClaw gateway flow — one clear path.
%% A message goes from you, through the gateway, to a model and its tools,
%% and every step lands in the logs. Render at https://mermaid.live
flowchart TD
    U[User<br/><i>you</i>] --> T[Telegram<br/><i>your channel</i>]
    T --> G{{Gateway<br/><b>the brain stem</b>}}
    G --> M[Model<br/><i>any provider</i>]
    M --> X[MCP Tools<br/><i>on a leash</i>]
    X --> L[(Logs<br/><i>every action</i>)]
    G -.-> L

    classDef hub fill:#0e2230,stroke:#22D3EE,stroke-width:2px,color:#E7EEFB;
    class G hub;
